## 3. Frameworks & Libraries

- **UI:** WordPress Gutenberg blocks authored in **JSX**, built with
  **`@wordpress/scripts`** (`^32`). Editor React comes from `@wordpress/*` packages
  (auto-detected into each `*.asset.php`). **No standalone React/Vue app.**
- **Styling:** **Tailwind CSS v3** only (admin/editor **and** front end). No CSS
  Modules, no Styled Components, no Sass.
- **Build:** `webpack.config.js` (wp-scripts) compiles `src/<name>/` →
  `build/<name>/` (and `build/components/<name>/`), plus two non-block editor-plugin
  entries: `template-reuse` (Remote Templates sidebar) and `content-io` (per-post
  Import/Export sidebar). `block-registry.php` scans `build/` **recursively** and
  registers every dir containing a `block.json`.
- **Commands:** `npm run build` (= `build:js` + `build:css`); `npm run dev` (JS watch +
  CSS watch); `npm run bundle` (distributable zip → `bundle/mbn-theme.zip`, dev/AI
  harness excluded). **Run `npm run build` after changing block source.** `build/`,
  `assets/build/` and `bundle/` are generated artifacts (gitignored); on a specific
  project install the `src/mbn-ai-*` sources ARE committed (see `development.md`).
- **Server:** PHP 8, WordPress theme. PHP indent 2 spaces (`phpcs.xml`);
  `composer run lint` must pass before commit.

